                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Remote / Maine</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Works with operators who have difficulty with traditional banks.</p>
                <a href="mailto:lending@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email Greenbridge Finance →</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dir-category">
            <div class="category-header">
              <h3>⚖️ Legal & Licensing</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="dir-list">
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>Tammie Snow, Esq.</strong>
                  <span class="verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> OCP licensing, municipal opt-in, regulatory compliance</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Portland, ME</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Former OCP stakeholder. Handles all license types.</p>
                <a href="mailto:legal@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email Tammie Snow →</a>
              </div>
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>Bernstein Shur</strong>
                  <span class="verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> Corporate law, zoning, business formation</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Portland / Augusta</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Large firm with dedicated cannabis practice group.</p>
                <a href="mailto:legal@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email Bernstein Shur →</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dir-category">
            <div class="category-header">
              <h3>📊 Accounting & Tax</h3>
              <span class="category-sponsor">Sponsored by Macpage</span>
            </div>
            <div class="dir-list">
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>BerryDunn</strong>
                  <span class="verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> 280E tax strategy, audit defense, bookkeeping</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Portland, ME</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Large regional firm. Deep cannabis 280E expertise.</p>
                <a href="mailto:accounting@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email BerryDunn →</a>
              </div>
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>Macpage</strong>
                  <span class="featured-tag">★ Featured</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> Financial strategy, CFO services, payroll</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> South Portland, ME</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Offers fractional CFO services for growing operators.</p>
                <a href="mailto:accounting@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email Macpage →</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dir-category">
            <div class="category-header">
              <h3>🏢 Real Estate & Zoning</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="dir-list">
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>CBRE Maine</strong>
                  <span class="featured-tag">★ Featured</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> Commercial real estate, dispensary buildouts, lease negotiations</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Portland</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> National firm with local Maine presence. Knows opt-in municipalities.</p>
                <a href="mailto:realestate@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email CBRE Maine →</a>
              </div>
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>Thebes Commercial</strong>
                  <span class="verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> Maine cannabis-specific real estate, sale-leasebacks</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Remote / Maine</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Focuses exclusively on Maine cannabis operators.</p>
                <a href="mailto:realestate@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email Thebes Commercial →</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dir-category">
            <div class="category-header">
              <h3>🔒 Security & Surveillance</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="dir-list">
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>Guardian Alarm Systems</strong>
                  <span class="verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> OCP-compliant security systems, 24/7 monitoring, installation</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Augusta, ME</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Approved vendor for multiple Maine dispensaries.</p>
