                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Scarborough, ME</p>
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> 5 completed Maine dispensary builds. Knows local codes.</p>
                <a href="mailto:build@mainedispensaryguide.com" class="dir-contact">Email Pine State Builders →</a>
              </div>
              <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-header">
                  <strong>Coastal Construction Group</strong>
                  <span class="verified-tag">✓ Verified</span>
                </div>
